Date: 1996-10-22

Title: Anomaly and Condensate in the Light-Cone Schwinger Model

Authors: J. Gamboa, I. Schmidt, L. Vergara

Comments: 10pp, Revtex

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B412 (1997) 111-118

The axial anomaly and fermion condensate in the light cone Schwinger modelare studied following path integral methods. This formalism allows for a simpleand direct calculation for these and other vacuum dependent phenomena.